title: definevalue
author: definevalue
content: My github is definevalue most my repos are just forks of projects i disassembled and put back together. I'm looking for either simple freelance gigs/oppourtunities I can provide consulting and handle the back-end an server management for your blockchain project. Private Enterprise ChainsReact AppsSolidity LogicTrading BotsCoin DevelopmentToken/NFT DevelopmentProvably-Fair GamesDefi Perp. Future MarketsCentralized ExchangesYou name it I have been involved with it one way or another. First 10 people I will give 30min free consultations on your business model and idea just for some relative feedback in this thread.
